{"id":171607,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/智利学生抗议（多图）/","date":"2011-08-11T16:00:27Z","modified":"2017-02-06T18:34:46Z","title":"智利学生抗议（多图）","content":"<p>原作者：<br />\n来源<a href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/infocus/2011/08/student-protests-in-chile/100125/\">焦点视野 &#8211; 智利学生抗议（多图）</a><br />\n译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/141320\">余游玩水</a></p>\n<p><span>在过去的几个月里，智利师生及支持者举行游行示威以抗议政府，此举旨在改革国家的教育制度。尤其是，为增加教育投入改善公立教育质量寻求公民投票。学生们以多种形式参与到抗议中，绝食，静坐，游行，枕头战。有小批抗议者与防暴警察发生正面冲突，投掷石块和燃烧弹。智利当局禁止游行示威，用高压水枪予以回击，并提出早前曾拒绝的教育建议。在未经政府许可的情况下，上万名学生在智利民众的广泛支持下，继续游行示威活动，反对总统</span><a><span><span>塞巴斯蒂安</span></span></a><span><span><span>·</span></span></span><span><span><span>皮涅拉</span></span></span><span>的民众呼声日益增高。以下图片记录了过去的几个月中，智利街头的景象。</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c01_07034159.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span>1.<span> </span></span></span><span>智利首都圣地亚哥，学生们举行游行示威要求政府开放免费的优质公立教育</span><span> 2011.8.7 </span><span>（美联社图片</span><span>/Aliosha Marquez</span><span>）</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c02_05162607.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><a><span><span>2.<span> <span> </span></span></span></span><span>学生与防暴警察在教育部外扭打在一起</span><span> 2011.7.5 </span></a><span><span>星期二</span> </span><span><span>美联社图片</span><span>/Luis Hidalgo</span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c03_RTR2PM4T.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span>3.圣地亚哥，防暴警察使用高压水枪对付集会中要求改变公立教育制度的学生抗议者。</span><span>2011.8.4</span><span>（路透社</span><span>/Victor Ruiz Caballero)</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c04_20383320.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> </span></p>\n<p><span><span>4.<span> </span></span></span><span>阿根廷和智利学生向位于布宜诺斯艾利斯的智利领事馆行进</span><span>，反对警察镇压在圣地亚哥举行游行示威的智利学生。2011.8.5（</span><span>Maxi Failla/</span><span>法新社</span><span>/</span><span>盖蒂图片社）</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c05_06077069.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span>5.<span> </span></span></span><span>圣地亚哥，</span><span>500</span><span>多名学生聚集在阿马斯广场，情侣们通过热吻的方式展现自己的教育激情。</span><span> 2011.7.6.</span><span>（美联社图片</span><span>/Aliosha Marquez</span><span>）</span></p>\n<p><a></a><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c06_RTR2O0KX.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span>6.<span> </span></span></span><span>智利瓦尔帕莱索的一次集会中，一个戴头巾的学生，用弹弓向防暴警察投掷石块。</span><span>2011.6.23.</span><span>（路透社</span><span>/Eliseo Fernandez</span><span>）</span></p>\n<p><span><span><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c07_04035761.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span>7.<span> </span></span></span><span>圣地亚哥的学生示威中，一名警察逃离戴着帽子的抗议者们的石块攻击。</span><span>2011.8.4</span><span>（美联社图片</span><span>/Roberto Candia)</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c08_52104218.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>8.<span> </span></span></span><span>瓦尔帕莱索，总统</span><span><span>塞巴斯蒂安</span></span><span><span>·</span></span><span><span>皮涅拉</span></span><span>正在向国会发表国情咨文演讲，而在国会附近的一场冲突中，游行示威者试图阻止警方的高压水车。</span><span>2011.5.21.</span><span>（美联社图片</span><span>/Carlos Vera</span><span>）</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c09_RTR2PRJH.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span>9.<span> </span></span></span><span>加入到要求公立教育制度改革的学生集会中的人们。</span><span>2011.8.9.</span><span>（路透社</span><span>/Ivan Alvarado</span><span>）</span><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c10_16114283.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span>10.<span> </span></span></span><span>2011.6.16</span><span>，圣地亚哥拉莫内达宫附近的一起抗议中，一名 裹着头巾的示威者正在躲避警察高压水枪的攻击。在要求无差别教育以及反对政府改革并私有化部分教育体系计划的抗议中，上千名学生和教授进行罢工（课）并与警察发生冲突。（美联社图片</span><span>/Roberto Candia</span><span>）</span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c11_RTR2PE08.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span>11.<span> </span></span></span><span>圣地亚哥，在要求变革公立教育制度的一起集会上，学生们和狗遭到水枪攻击。</span><span>2011.7.28.( </span><span>路透社</span><span>/Carlos Vera) </span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c12_RTR2PRYP.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span>12.<span> </span></span></span><span>瓦尔帕莱索的要求公立教育制度改革的抗议政府集会上，学生们敲打着餐具。</span><span>2011.8.9.</span><span>（路透社</span><span>/Eliseo Fernandez</span><span>）</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c13_RTR2O87M.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> </span></p>\n<p><span><span><span> </span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>13.<span> </span></span></span><span>“以教育之名集体自杀”的抗议中，学生们在大声呼喊，他们躺在瓦尔帕莱索街头，要求政府对教育制度作出变革。</span><span>2011.6.28.</span><span>（路透社</span><span>/Eliseo Fernandez</span><span>）</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c14_RTR2PMLA.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span>14.圣地亚哥的一起集会中，消防员正设法扑灭吞没了百货大楼的大火。学生们组织集会要求变革公立教育制度。路透社不能证实此次大火是否为抗议者所为。</span><span>2011.8.4.</span><span>（路透社</span><span>/Carlos Vera<span>）</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c15_RTR2PRJP.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>15.<span> </span></span></span><span>要求改革公立教育制度的学生集会中，站岗的防爆警察。</span><span>2011.8.9.</span><span>墙上写着“智利，你唯利是图”。（路透社</span><span>/Ivan Alvarado</span><span>）</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c16_RTR2PM6O.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span>16.<span> </span></span></span><span>抗议集会中，一名学生被警察扣留。</span><span>2011.8.4.</span><span>（路透社</span><span>/Carlos Vera</span><span>）</span></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c17_30045703.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span>17.<span> </span></span></span><span>一名示威者准备向利用高压水枪射击的警方，投掷自制的燃烧弹。</span><span>2011.6.30.</span><span>（美联社图片</span><span>/Luis Hidalgo</span><span>）</span></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c18_12122901.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span>18.<span> </span></span></span><span>在圣地亚哥市中心的游行示威中，智利学生遭到警察高压水枪的喷射。</span><span>2011.5.12.(</span><span>美联社图片</span><span>/Roberto Candia)</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c19_09148809.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>19.  圣地亚哥，骚乱中，同行示威者放火烧毁一辆汽车。抗议活动后，一名示威者坐在翻倒的汽车旁边的沙发上。2011.8.9.（美联社图片/Sebastian Silva）<br />\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c20_RTR2N65P.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>20.  圣地亚哥市中心的集会上，一名学生被防爆警察的高压水柱击中。2011.6.1.(路透社/Ivan Alvarado)<br />\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c21_09146639.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>21.  圣地亚哥市中心，学生抗议活动过后，头戴面具的示威者站在一处燃烧的路障旁。2011.8.9.(美联社图片/Sebastian Silva)<br />\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c22_RTR2OHUT.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>22.  2011.7.5，圣地亚哥进行罢课的学生们睡在Liceo 1 学校里。学生们参加静坐示威以继续抗议要求智利的中右翼政府通过改善教育质量，降低学费以及免费公交车的决议。（路透社/Victor Ruiz Caballero）<br />\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c23_RTR2PCHH.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>23.  2011.7.27，圣地亚哥绝食抗议的第七天，Liceo Dario Salas的一名学生躺在地面上。29个来自国内不同高校的学生们，进行绝食示威要求政府改革公立教育制度。（路透社/Victor Ruiz Caballero）<br />\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c24_RTR2PRQ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>24.  瓦尔帕莱索，在要求改革公立教育制度的抗议中，学生们在投掷石块。2011.8.9.(路透社/Eliseo Fernandez)<br />\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c25_RTR2PRRE.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>25. 瓦尔帕莱索，反政府集会中，防暴警察追赶学生。2011.8.9.(路透社/Eliseo Fernandez)<br />\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c26_RTR2P0XP.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>26. 圣地亚哥，学生们扮成超人，抗议政府。2011.7.18.(路透社/Victor Ruiz Caballero)<br />\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c27_RTR2PRIR.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>27. 人们在自家敲打烹饪厨具，以大声抗议的形式支持智利学生要求政府改革公立教育制度的集会。2011.8.9.(路透社/Ivan Alvarado)<br />\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c28_RTR2OUJ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>28. 瓦尔帕莱索，学生们参加“为最好的教育而战”的集体枕头大战，以抗议政府。2011.7.13.（路透社/Eliseo Fernandez）<br />\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c29_RTR2PRR4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>29  瓦尔帕莱索的反政府集会中，学生们向由燃烧弹引燃的防暴车投掷石块。2011.8.9.（路透社/Eliseo Fernandez）<br />\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c30_RTR2PRMI.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>30. 圣地亚哥，学生抗议活动中，示威者躲避水柱。2011.8.9.（路透社/Carlos Vera）<br />\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cdn.theatlantic.com/static/infocus/chileprotest081011/s_c31_09159251.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>31. 圣地亚哥，学生抗议活动后，一名带着面具的示威者站在骚乱中引燃的翻倒车